title: AUSTIN MCBROOM SAYS HE’LL KNOCKOUT BRYCE HALL — BFFs EP. 33
description:
Austin McBroom joins us in Miami to talk about his upcoming Bryce Hall fight. Austin talks about the scuffle with Jake Paul that happened at the BFFs house, how he plans on knocking out Bryce, and what’s next for his future in boxing.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/bffspod
